<v-navigation-drawer
    id="app-drawer"
    v-model="inputValue"
    app
    dark 
    floating
    persistent
    mobile-break-point="991"
    width="260"
  >
   <v-list  style="background: none;">
     <v-list-item>
	   <v-img
	     :src="logo"
	     height="34"
		 width="34"
	     style="background: none;margin-right: 15px;"
	   />
       <v-list-item-title class="title">
         量化大师
       </v-list-item-title>
     </v-list-item>
     <v-divider class="my-2" />
     <v-list-item
       v-for="(link, i) in links"
       :key="i"
       :to="link.to"
	   color="green"
       class="v-list-item my-0"
     >
       <v-list-item-action>
		   <Avatar :src="iconArr[link.icon]" />
         <!-- <v-icon>{{ link.icon }}</v-icon> -->
       </v-list-item-action>
	   
       <v-list-item-title
         v-text="link.text"
       />
     </v-list-item>
   </v-list>
   <v-footer
	  absolute
         class="font-weight-medium py-2 grey darken-3"
       >
         <v-col
           class="text-center grey--text darken-2"
           cols="12"
         >
           版本：v1.0.1
         </v-col>
       </v-footer>
   
  </v-navigation-drawer>
